+## Run The Local Web UI
+
+Use `hive setup` when you want the TUI and web UI pointed at the same local XDG/Hive state:
+
+```bash
+cd ~/Dev/your-project
+hive setup
+open http://127.0.0.1:4567
+```
+
+For foreground debugging:
+
+```bash
+hive web --port 4570
+```
+
+For managed lifecycle without rerunning setup:
+
+```bash
+hive web install
+hive web start
+hive web status --json
+```
+
+The local default is loopback no-auth. To expose the web UI on another interface, configure GitHub owner auth or pass the explicit unsafe no-auth flag for a trusted private network only.
